{"tid":1169221,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[唔知wow咗未]用flipster免費睇E-Magazine","createTime":"2019-05-24T08:33:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-24T08:53:37.000Z","uid":66753,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c185d348fce5bd0955598d4b28c02f2526ae378e","tid":1169221,"uid":66753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T08:33:54.000Z","msg":"可能好多巴絲都知公共圖書館有hyread，down個apps或用web版，<br />\n都算多中文書同雜誌網上睇/借，<br />\n其實另外上年定前年圖書館都引入咗flipster，<br />\n畀市民睇Time,bloomberg,national geographic 等英文雜誌（不過冇economist)，<br />\n仲有好多種類，想學英文可以揀啲生活化少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只要log in返acc就可以，用tablet睇都幾方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/05/24/162858_c98e0715970bdb820257e4b704205945.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F05%2F24%2F162858_c98e0715970bdb820257e4b704205945.png&h=1f81df45&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/05/24/162902_730acf1fe4d2e6313ca392fcacfa3566.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F05%2F24%2F162902_730acf1fe4d2e6313ca392fcacfa3566.png&h=8b331bff&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"388d647564ef224fac0d3030e83f89bdcbf90aa8","tid":1169221,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T08:36:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86af056a8fd98df1e0bca6ff368d19ba4680d1c1","tid":1169221,"uid":66753,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T08:53:37.000Z","msg":"補充：Flipster要先入咗web version set up 新UID先可以再喺apps搵HK public libraries登入，唔似hyread咁自動link返去HKPL。<br />\napps可以借雜誌offline睇，借閱日子視乎邊本"}]}